					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Games wait for vblank.  Then they don't care how few objects there are on the screen.  You only get a problem with slowdown when there are too many objects.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Here come the fortune cookies!  Here come the fortune cookies!  They're wearing paper hats!</div>
