			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The PPU's job is to make a TV picture out of what it sees in its memory.<br />It's making 240 visible scanlines of picture, and 26 lines of Vblank between the frames.  (there's also some horizontal and vertical sync pulses in there too)<br />It knows which scanline it's processing, and what it's doing.  When it finishes drawing the 240 lines of picture, it starts making vblank for the TV.  One scanline later it generates a non-maskable interrupt (NMI).<br />That's the interrupt that the game uses.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Here come the fortune cookies!  Here come the fortune cookies!  They're wearing paper hats!</div>
